name: Dread
content:
"Dread" was the callsign of a First Order TIE/se Bomber pilot and was devoted to destruction. "Dread" once flew their bomber in a battle between TIE line starfighters and T-70 X-wing starfighters.
"Dread " was created for the miniatures game Star Wars: X-Wing Second Edition in the card of the same name released in the 2021 Fury of the First Order Squadron Pack.
